    "description": "<p>SealXpert Products Pte Ltd is headquartered in Singapore and with offices in Hong Kong and Indonesia.</p>\n\n<p>SealXpert is a dynamic and fast-growing company.  The company manufacturers and distributes industrial <u>M</u>aintenance, <u>R</u>epair and  <u>O</u>perations (MRO) consumables including Leak Repair & Reinforcement, Corrosion Protection, Repair Putties and Coatings, Adhesives, Sealants & Special Lubricants.</p>\n\n<p>Currently SealXpert products are sold in more than 50 countries worldwide spanning Asia, Europe, Middle East and America. Our products are widely used in the Oil & Gas, Petrochemical, Chemical, Power Generation, Marine & Offshore, Utilities and Facilities Management Industries.</p>\n",
